 - Add key mapping for g~ (Ng~.).
 - Bug: "kilo^mét" (kilômét)
 - Bug: "xoa" (xoá) in rich text editors, including Thunderbird and Composer.
 - Automatically convert q<[aeioy]> -> qu, g<e> -> gh, ng<[ei]> -> ngh, etc.
